00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,000
i cal aconseguir el repte.

243
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:05,000
Plàcid matí,

244
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:07,000
caminant pel Rosselló.

245
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,000
Una comarca que forma part del departament francès

246
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:11,000
dels Pirineus Orientals,

247
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,000
des de 1659,

248
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:15,000
quan es va signar el Tractat dels Pirineus.

249
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,000
L'impressionant massís

250
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:19,000
d'Alcanigó domina la plana

251
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:21,000
alçant-se fins als 2.784 m

252
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,000
des de cota zero

253
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:25,000
en només 20 km.

254
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:27,000
Aquesta distància entre la base

255
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:29,000
i el pic s'anomena Prominència

256
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,000
i l'Alcanigó és de les més grans

257
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,000
del Pirineu.

258
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:35,000
Vola ternera. A veure si podem aconseguir

259
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,000
el repte d'avui. Us recordo que

260
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:39,000
m'estic plantejant una espècie de desafiament

261
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,000
per cada país que passi

262
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,000
i el de França consisteix en menjar un croissant

263
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:45,000
cada dia. El d'ahir

264
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,000
estava boníssim.

265
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:49,000
No estic trobant res.

266
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:51,000
És que el poble és molt petit.

267
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:53,000
Ah, mira, li preguntarem aquesta malla aquí.

268
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:55,000
Perdona, perdona, que parles català?

269
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:57,000
Hola, i tant. Mira, sóc catalana jo.

270
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,000
Ets d'aquí, de Catalunya Nord?

271
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:01,000
No, sóc de Barcelona, és de la Pixapina.

272
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:03,000
Ah, mira, ja som dos.

273
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:05,000
Ah, mira, que bé, dos pixapins que es la troben.

274
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:07,000
Mira, estic fent un vídeo de YouTube.

275
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:09,000
Ah, mira. T'importa sortir?

276
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:11,000
No, no, encantada, encantada.

277
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,000
Com et dius? Maria Rosa.

278
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:15,000
Encantat, Maria Rosa. Igualment.

279
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:17,000
Mira, que estic en ruta

280
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,000
per França. Sí, molt bé.

281
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:21,000
I m'estic plantejant un repte personal, diari,

282
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:23,000
que és menjar un croissant cada dia

283
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,000
ja que estic a França. Ah, caram.

284
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:27,000
Ho has aconseguit fins ara? Sí.

285
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,000
Sí, molt bé. Molt bons.

286
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,000
Però clar, aquí en aquest poble trobo que

287
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:33,000
està tot tancat. És que avui és festiu,

288
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:35,000
no, ahir? No, i és festiu, està tot tancat.

289
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,000
Una fleca o algo. No, res de res.

290
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,000
Però no pateixis, perquè casualment

291
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,000
no. No. Casualment jo tinc uns croissants

292
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:43,000
que he comprat aquest matí

293
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,000
en un altre poble. No.

294
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:47,000
Ostres, com t'ho curres? I t'ajudaré

295
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:49,000
a aconseguir el teu repte.

296
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:51,000
Tot sigui pels teus seguidors, eh?

297
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,000
Uah. Pels teus seguidors.

298
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:55,000
M'has salvat. Pels teus seguidors.

299
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:57,000
M'has salvat. Mira, mira.

300
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,000
Quin bé de Déu de croissants. Ostres.

301
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:01,000
Ostres, que en podria agafar un? I tant.

302
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:03,000
El que més t'agradi. Ostres.

303
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:05,000
M'has salvat, m'has salvat. A veure.

304
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:07,000
Anem-hi ja.

305
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:09,000
Està bo? Mmm.

306
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,000
Repte aconseguit.

307
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:13,000
Deixant enrere bula ternera,

308
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:15,000
fotem-li canya a aquesta art

309
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:17,000
i vol ploure.

310
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:21,000
Una travessa tan llarga com aquesta

311
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,000
no la pots planificar al 100%.

312
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:25,000
Cada pas, cada quilòmetre, cada camí...

313
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,000
Tens una idea general

314
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:29,000
d'on vols anar, però cada dia t'enfrentes

315
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:31,000
a desenes de decisions.

316
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,000
Com ara.

317
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:35,000
El camí que havia traçat inicialment

318
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:37,000
va per aquesta carretera.

319
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:39,000
Camí segur, sense cap problema.

320
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:41,000
Però,

321
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:43,000
he vist aquest d'aquí

322
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:45,000
ascendint-se per mig del bosc

323
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:47,000
i sembla més maco, no trobaré cotxes.

324
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:49,000
Potser faig una mica més de volta,

325
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,000
però una mica d'aventura no ha matat mai a ningú, no?

326
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:53,000
M'arrisco.

327
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:59,000
Bé, potser el camí

328
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:01,000
ara s'ha tornat una mica recrescut.

329
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:03,000
Bé, no passa res.

330
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,000
Formar part de l'aventura, també.

331
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:07,000
Això no es troba al planning.

332
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,000
Hauria de fer cas al track

333
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:11,000
i ara com surto d'aquí.

334
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:13,000
Re.

335
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:15,000
Retirada.

336
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:17,000
Retirada per on he vingut

337
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:19,000
i he perdut 20 minuts.

338
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:21,000
Conclusió.

339
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:23,000
Seguir el track és de covards,

340
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:25,000
però a vegades és útil.

341
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:37,000
Pujada costeruda

342
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:39,000
i ventosa fins aquí.

343
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:41,000
Però ha valgut la pena, tu.

344
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:43,000
Vistes espectaculars

345
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:45,000
de tot el Rosselló.

346
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:47,000
D'allà venim,

347
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:49,000
del massís del Canigó.

348
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,000
Hem travessat tota la vall,

349
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:53,000
hem pujat fins aquí

350
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:55,000
i mireu, allò és Perpinyà

351
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:57,000
i allò d'allà és la llacuna de Salses.

352
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:59,000
És una llacuna costera bastant gran.

353
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:01,000
Tan gran som tenim a Catalunya.

354
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:03,000
Aquesta té la particularitat

355
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:05,000
que fa 15 anys una empresa europea

356
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:07,000
que no hi era ni.

357
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:09,000
Però els van enxampar i els van posar una multa.

358
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:11,000
Encara prendreu alguna cosa i tot.

359
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:13,000
Vinga, últim track del dia d'avui.

360
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:15,000
Ara ja, tot baixada.

361
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:31,000
Doncs ja ho tindríem, el dia d'avui.

362
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:33,000
Que és a les 8 de la tarda,

363
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:35,000
es va fent fosc.

364
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:37,000
I ara a campar.

365
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,000
He mirat la vista satèl·lit

366
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:41,000
i aquí semblava que era bastant pla

367
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:43,000
i bastant amagadet.

368
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:45,000
Mireu, aniré cap allà a veure que tal.

369
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,000
Aquí està perfecte, tu.

370
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:49,000
Plantaré aquí.

371
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,000
Doncs no ha sigut un bon dia, al final.

372
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:09,000
Ni pluja, ni vent,

373
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:11,000
ni senglars,

374
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:13,000
ni ciclistes enfurismats.

375
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:15,000
Ara ho veureu en pantalla.

376
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:17,000
Han sortit 39 quilòmetres.

377
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,000
Déu n'hi do.

378
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:21,000
900 metres de senyall positiu.

379
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:23,000
Dia bastant fort, al final.

380
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:25,000
Ara, com cada dia, toca encendre el foc.

381
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:27,000
I, mentre va fent el sopar,

382
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:29,000
vaig contestant alguna

383
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:31,000
de les vostres preguntes.

384
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:33,000
La Pepita Pons em pregunta

385
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:35,000
